{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6eee849447","title":"给张治中的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3c644c5382","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"6eee849447"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"fb0b18eb66","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张治中1958年5月3日给毛泽东的信。信中谈了他在民革整风期间写的《自我检查》的情况，并将《自我检查》和他1949年冬写的《六十岁总结》送请毛泽东审阅。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3058c7298b","type":"title","text":"给张治中的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"fb0b18eb66","type":"paragraph","text":"文白先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"dcef7bb102","type":"paragraph","text":"五月三日的信早已收到。原封不动，直至今天，打升一看，一口气读完了《六十岁总结》，感到高兴。我的高兴，不是在你的世界观方面。在这方面，我们是有距离的。高兴是在作品的气氛方面，是在使人能看到作者的心的若十点方面，是在你还有向前进取的意愿方面。我猜想，这一年多的时间内，害苦了你，一个老人遇到这样的大风浪。这种心情，我是理解的。觅暇当约大驾一谈。这几天尚不可能。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"204256cf16","type":"paragraph","text":"祝安好！问候你的关人和孩子们","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"1a45c19b2f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"94dbecd575","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十二日上午七时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"},{"id":"dcf60e714f","type":"paragraph","text":"11]张治中，字文白，当时任全国人大常委会委员、国防委员会副主席。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447"}],"page":{"id":"70747be6e3","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6eee849447","start":362,"end":362}}}},"__N_SSG":true}